---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Spot AI Cameras | AI-Powered Video Surveillance — Blue Cap IT" description="Spot AI provides premium AI-powered IP cameras at no cost, or works with your existing cameras. Camera-agnostic platform that upgrades any ONVIF-compliant camera with AI video intelligence.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/spotai/spotai-logo.png" alt="Spot AI" style="max-height:50px;width:auto;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"/>
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="spotai.html">Spot AI</a> <span>/</span> AI Cameras</div>
      <div class="section-label">Spot AI Platform</div>
      <h1>AI-Powered <span class="grad">Cameras</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Spot AI is fully camera-agnostic — it works with your existing IP cameras and can provide premium cameras at no additional cost. Every camera connected to the platform instantly gains AI capabilities including object detection, people counting, and intelligent search.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Camera Flexibility</div>
          <h2>Keep Your Cameras.<br/><span class="grad">Add AI.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">You don't need to rip and replace your entire camera system. Spot AI connects to any ONVIF-compliant IP camera through the Intelligent Video Recorder, instantly upgrading them with deep-learning AI capabilities. Or choose Spot AI's premium cameras — included at no additional cost with your subscription.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">📷</div>
            <div><h4>Free Premium Cameras</h4><p>Spot AI provides premium IP cameras at no additional cost with your platform subscription. High-quality hardware, zero upfront expense.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔄</div>
            <div><h4>Use Existing Cameras</h4><p>Any ONVIF-compliant IP camera works with Spot AI. Upgrade your current investment with AI — no hardware replacement needed.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔍</div>
            <div><h4>Auto-Discovery</h4><p>The Intelligent Video Recorder auto-discovers cameras on your network, ingests video streams, encrypts them, and indexes every frame.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🧠</div>
            <div><h4>Instant AI Upgrade</h4><p>The moment a camera connects, deep-learning models begin classifying people, vehicles, objects, and motion — making footage searchable and actionable.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Upgrade Your Cameras <span class="grad">With AI</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT to deploy Spot AI with your existing cameras or get premium cameras included at no cost.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
